title: Clive Barkers Hellraiser (01 - 20 + Extra) (2011 - 2012) (Digita
description:
Clive Barkers Hellraiser (01 - 20 + Extra) (2011 - 2012) (Digital) (Minutemen-PhD) 


Hellraiser returns to comics in this new volume co-written by Clive Barker himself; putting his own hand to this long-running franchise he created for only the third time (after the original novel and writing/directing the first movie).

The new series draws from "classic continuity", though if this includes the 90's Marvel/Epic comics or just the earlier movies isn't yet entirely clear.
